Catalano.Imaging.Tools

Class ColorConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • Catalano.Imaging.Tools.ColorConverter

  • public class ColorConverter
extends java.lang.Object
    Convert between different color spaces supported. RGB -> IHS -> RGB RGB -> CMYK -> RGB RGB -> YIQ -> RGB RGB -> YCbCr -> RGB RGB -> YUV -> RGB RGB -> RGChromaticity RGB -> HSV -> RGB RGB -> YCC -> RGB RGB -> YCoCg -> RGB RGB -> XYZ -> RGB RGB -> HunterLAB -> RGB RGB -> HLS -> RGB RGB -> CIE-LAB -> RGB XYZ -> HunterLAB -> XYZ XYZ -> CIE-LAB -> XYZ
